title: [Vineyard Path, Crossing]
description: Four spiraling paths curve around large, rounded granite boulders that sparkle with flecks of mica and feldspar.  They burst from a circular mosaic depicting the image of Kuon tending a garden.  Small votives glow from nooks and crannies on the faces of the boulders.
paths: Obvious paths: northeast, southeast, southwest, northwest
